726763f-a.title: Queens: Grand Avenue - Van Loon Street
726763f-a.text:
Grand Avenue, south side, east of Van Loon Street to Queens
Boulevard. The spire at the right is a section of the First
Fresbyterian Church of Newtown.
March 1923
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
